okup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-214">Since this will not usually be the case, the method will nearly always return `false` even if there is an object in the collection with exactly the same values in all its properties as the object passed to the **Contains** method of <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c43d8-215">の<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>内容を確認するには、各メンバーを目的の値と比較して列挙する必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-215">To determine the contents of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>, you must enumerate through each of its members, comparing them with the desired value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c43d8-216">例を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-216">See the example.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c43d8-217"><xref:System.Printing.PageResolution>クラスには、X および Y 次元に対して1インチあたりのドット数と、解像度に定性式を指定できるプロパティがあります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-217">The <xref:System.Printing.PageResolution> class has properties in which you can specify the dots-per-inch for the X and Y dimensions and a property where you can give a qualitative expression to the resolution.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c43d8-218">プリンターでページ解像度の選択肢がサポートされていない場合、コレクションは空になります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-218">If the printer does not support page resolution choices, the collection is empty.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c43d8-219">このプロパティは、[印刷スキーマ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)の`PageResolution`キーワードに対応します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-219">This property corresponds to the [Print Schema](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)'s `PageResolution` keyword.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c43d8-220">次のコード例は、 <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>で特定の値を検索する方法を示しています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c43d8-220">The following code example shows how to search for a particular value in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
foreach (PageResolution pageRes in pc.PageResolutionCapability)  
    {  
        if (pageRes.QualitativeResolution == PageQualitativeResolution.High)  
        {  
            Console.WriteLine("High quality is supported");  
            break;  
        }  
    }  
```
